---
title: Chermoula Spiced Chickpeas with Honey Roasted Pumpkin Couscous & Pickled Onion Salsa
description: It’s time to up your legume game and we're going to show you how. Transform the humble chickpea with a little spice  and crushed tomatoes, making a perfect topping for pumpkin couscous. Add pickled onion for zing, and dinner is done!
